
These are test roms for emulator_test.

Only two are included in the repository:
  escape.nes is Adam Goode's port of my GPL game Escape to NES.
  test1.nes is a hand-made test cartridge that runs many exotic
     instructions. You can find the source code in ../../grad/cart.

The others are not hard to find, but of course they are copyrighted
so they are not distributed with fceulib.

